ic ways to leverage your efforts through&lt;br /&gt;effective networking, this text presents a soup-to-nuts approach to marketing your business and 'making rain',"&lt;br /&gt;says Graham. "Coaching brings the book to life and it becomes more than just another piece of information -- it becomes an actionable strategy to increase your your gross sales."&lt;br&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br /&gt;The Mastermind Group works through each book slowly – one text about every three months – so participants can&lt;br /&gt;easily keep up with the reading. In addition to providing meeting space, members of the group receive 20% off the&lt;br /&gt;text from Borders.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;iframe src="http://rcm.amazon.com/e/cm?t=trueazimuth-20&amp;amp;o=1&amp;amp;p=8&amp;amp;l=as1&amp;amp;asins=0814472168&amp;amp;fc1=000000&amp;amp;IS2=1&amp;amp;lt1=_blank&amp;amp;m=amazon&amp;amp;lc1=0000FF&amp;amp;bc1=000000&amp;amp;bg1=FFFFFF&amp;amp;f=ifr" style="width: 120px; height: 240px;" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no" frameborder="0"&gt;&lt;/iframe&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;hr&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;True Azimuth, LLC, headquartered in West Fairlee, Vermont, began offering business, personal and relationship&lt;br /&gt;coaching in 2006. For more information about the Mastermind Group, call 802-380-1026 or go to&lt;br /&gt;&lt;a href="http://Mastermind.TrueAzimuth.biz"&gt;http://Mastermind.TrueAzimuth.biz&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;p style="text-align: right;"&gt;&lt;span style="font-size: 0.8em; color: #666666;"&gt;©2009 True Azimuth, LLC&lt;br&gt;&lt;a href="http://trueazimuth.biz/"&gt;Business Coaching&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="http://trueazimuth.biz/"&gt;Relationship Coaching&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href="http://trueazimuth.biz/"&gt;Life Coaching&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br/&gt;&lt;div class="blogger-post-footer"&gt;&lt;img width='1' height='1' src='https://blo